text: Muldashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilchigulovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 81 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 105 km from Uchaly, 10 km from Ilchigulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Muldashevo
